sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist<br/>(Jupyter Notebook)
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant OAuth as OAuth Proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant API as API Server<br/>8888/TCP HTTP (internal TLS)
    participant DB as MariaDB<br/>3306/TCP MySQL
    participant S3 as Minio/S3<br/>9000/443 TCP
    participant SWF as Scheduled Workflow Controller
    participant WFC as Workflow Controller<br/>Argo
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Pod as Workflow Pod
    participant PA as Persistence Agent
    participant MLMD as ML Metadata gRPC<br/>8080/TCP gRPC

    Note over User,MLMD: Flow 1: Pipeline Submission from Notebook

    User->>Route: POST /apis/v2beta1/pipelines<br/>Bearer Token (OAuth)
    Route->>OAuth: Forward request<br/>TLS 1.2+
    OAuth->>API: Validated request<br/>Internal TLS
    API->>DB: Store pipeline metadata<br/>TLS (if podToPodTLS=true)
    DB-->>API: Confirm
    API->>S3: Upload pipeline definition<br/>AccessKey/SecretKey
    S3-->>API: Artifact URL
    API-->>OAuth: Pipeline created (ID)
    OAuth-->>Route: Response
    Route-->>User: Pipeline ID + Status

    Note over User,MLMD: Flow 2: Workflow Execution

    SWF->>WFC: Create Workflow CR<br/>ServiceAccount
    WFC->>K8s: Create Workflow Pods<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8s-->>WFC: Pods scheduled
    WFC-->>Pod: Start execution
    Pod->>S3: Download input artifacts<br/>AccessKey/SecretKey
    S3-->>Pod: Artifacts
    Pod->>Pod: Execute pipeline step
    Pod->>MLMD: Log metadata<br/>mTLS (if podToPodTLS=true)
    MLMD-->>Pod: Metadata stored
    Pod->>S3: Upload output artifacts<br/>AccessKey/SecretKey
    S3-->>Pod: Confirm
    Pod-->>WFC: Step complete

    Note over User,MLMD: Flow 3: Workflow State Persistence

    PA->>K8s: Watch Workflow CRs<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8s-->>PA: Workflow state changes
    PA->>API: Update run status<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    API->>DB: Persist workflow state<br/>TLS (if podToPodTLS=true)
    DB-->>API: Confirm
    API-->>PA: Status updated

    Note over User,MLMD: Flow 4: UI Artifact Retrieval

    User->>Route: GET /pipeline-ui/<br/>OAuth Session
    Route->>OAuth: Validate session
    OAuth->>API: Fetch pipeline runs<br/>Bearer Token
    API->>DB: Query runs<br/>TLS (if podToPodTLS=true)
    DB-->>API: Run data
    API-->>OAuth: Pipeline runs
    OAuth-->>User: UI with runs
    User->>S3: GET artifact (presigned URL)<br/>Presigned Token
    S3-->>User: Artifact content
